source: TEXT_DUNGEONTAMTARA_00000_EDDA_000_000<tab>Look, Avere! All these people have come to make you a gift of their souls! Isn't that kind of them?
target: TEXT_DUNGEONTAMTARA_00000_EDDA_000_000<tab>Tous nos amis sont venus nous apporter des cadeaux pour célébrer notre bonheur, à Avere et à moi<var 1D /var>!
